Logo alignments were calculated using ggseqlogo, using either the pooled dataset or the dataset of recurring SNVs. Logo alignments of the human edited sites were performed using ADAR sites from REDIportal (

  48
 ) that were shared by at least four samples. SARS-CoV-2, SARS, and MERS genomic data were prepared for the Logi alignment using the GenomicRanges R package (

